{"tid":1458358,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係小小P，但想檢討同brainstorm下之後策略","createTime":"2019-08-12T13:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:58:30.000Z","uid":300922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2699270a1cee2d186fbcb8dff3371ca92a448b61","tid":1458358,"uid":300922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:46:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>1. 機場要去，但要諗下係米日日去，去又做咩好。</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n其實星期五至日都有和你飛，但無影響過機場運作，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為人數唔多</span></span>，唔夠阻嚇。今日係政府驚一驚，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">係無任何實際阻礙下</span></span>，自己停飛。但我地玩緊心理戰？我地想佢停飛，真停飛個時我地又會驚，然後撤。<br />\n<br />\n如果政府學精，唔停飛呢？和理非都攰，無可能日日都似今日咁多人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>2. 一日只要一場集會</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n其實之前幾週都好多和理非參與，但<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">毫無影響力</span></strong></strong></span>，原因係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非的影響力取決於人數</span></strong></span>。不斷分散只會消耗。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>3. 未諗到點認證係人係鬼前，請盡量搞多啲和理非活動</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n我絕對喜歡勇武，亦覺得係一場革命係需要武力，但原諒我真的只想減少傷亡。你即管罵我左膠。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">和非理集會亦需要勇武在場捉鬼，一旦有任何人企圖破壞非暴力氣氛，一定係鬼！一定係鬼！</span><br />\n<br />\n人數夠多的和理非活動，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>一來會減少傷亡，二來要打好公關（之前幾週完全無媒體報道過任何和理非的活動，只用無數暴力畫面製造更多恐慌），三來要告訴社會我們無割蓆，四來勇武要回氣要諗新對策，五來人數多必會有影響力，必會有。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外，小小提醒，<em><span style=\"color: violet;\">啲差佬分明要搞女仔</span></em>。麻煩各位絲打著返多少少布，tee shirt同長褲，飾物都唔好戴，盡量保護自己，差佬真係好賤！<br />\n<br />\n我只係個小小p，經驗或者唔夠，希望大家討論討論。"},{"pid":"5274f459e3816ee8056f5531ce36984f34127119","tid":1458358,"uid":300922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:49:12.000Z","msg":"自推幾下"},{"pid":"744f2c4e76a335ccd4f34db15cb14a64ea8e5026","tid":1458358,"uid":300922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:49:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f8fc2d0b3b9cdf801f3a91b8a973f148fd817a1","tid":1458358,"uid":300922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:49:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"369d68a0b3694d6ad26eaf2de34dedd9505e2587","tid":1458358,"uid":300922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:49:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80fc162c8a78262ac61d0d383f89389c09cf431e","tid":1458358,"uid":300922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:50:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"608c47a488a6917fd1b3727ff72db95ae031c581","tid":1458358,"uid":300922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:50:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f39f3c386978ef09317aa976146c1dc9c97d23b","tid":1458358,"uid":300922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:50:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdea9bc2d4a1831e20247b0c82b773ef1d0294b8","tid":1458358,"uid":300922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:58:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1383bbb8487eaa2647a41ed5a7f25639aa7a967","tid":1458358,"uid":300922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:58:30.000Z","msg":"推"}]}